content: One of my favorite discoveries from that playlist is the song "Take On Me" by A-ha, which I hadn't heard in years. I've also rediscovered my love for 80s synth-pop, which has led me to explore more music from that era. By the way, I've already saved about 20 songs to my personal Favorites playlist in the past 5 days from that playlist, so it's definitely been a great source of new music for me.
